## **4.3  Phase Instructions  (configs/config.yaml)**

### **Phase 1 — Analysis**

10. Parse usecase\_id, records, strategy\_results, notes from the user message.

11. Call evaluate\_optimization\_rules with the records.

12. Store evaluation results in Cosmos DB via store\_phase\_result('analysis\_phase').

13. Store input metadata in Cosmos DB via store\_phase\_result('input\_data').

### **Phase 2 — Report Generation**

14. Retrieve Phase 1 results from Cosmos DB via get\_phase\_result.

15. Call report\_generator to build a deterministic Markdown scaffold.

16. Polish the scaffold into a final executive Markdown report — Markdown only, no JSON or tool names.

17. Save the report to disk via export\_report.

# **5\. Prompt Definition & Passing**

## **5.1  Prompt Sources**

| \# | File | Type | Used In |
| :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | configs/config.yaml | System prompt | Every LLM call |
| 2 | configs/config.yaml | Phase 1 instructions | Phase 1 only |
